
    MainApp.java: Initializes the JavaFX application and loads the login page.
    LoginController.java: Validates login credentials and transitions to the capturing page.
    CaptureController.java: Starts and stops packet capturing, detects intrusions, and updates the TableView.
    IntrusionDetector.java: Interfaces with the Python model to analyze packet data.
    VisualizationController.java: Gathers statistics and updates graphical components.
    DatabaseManager.java: Handles CRUD operations with MongoDB.
    PacketData.java: Represents packet data structure for database storage.
    ThreatData.java: Represents threat data structure for database storage.
    PacketCapture.java: Captures packets from the network interface using Jpcap.

